ynthesizer, violin, viola, cello\n- phonk, russian dark accordion, russian psaltery, russian harmonica\n\n### 음성 유형\n- female voice\n- male voice\n- clean vocals\n- crystal-clear soprano voice\n- deep male voice\n\n### 전문 용어\n- 110 bpm, 140 bpm, 160 bpm (분당 비트 수 지정)\n- fast tempo\n- slow tempo\n- loops\n- fills\n- acoustic guitar\n- electric bass\n- G major, B flat major, D minor"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":108,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-542.4458044464902,-795.5231258173704],"size":[326.929504577269,371.40637875989955],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.5.1","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["## Model Links (for Local Users)\n\n**diffusion_models**\n\n- [acestep_v1.5_turbo.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/acestep_v1.5_turbo.safetensors)\n\n**text_encoders**\n\n- [qwen_0.6b_ace15.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_0.6b_ace15.safetensors)\n- [qwen_1.7b_ace15.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_1.7b_ace15.safetensors)\n\n**vae**\n\n- [ace_1.5_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ace_1.5_vae.safetensors)\n\n\n## Model Storage Location\n\n```\n📂 ComfyUI/\n├── 📂 models/\n│   ├── 📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │   └── acestep_v1.5_turbo.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 text_encoders/\n│   │   ├── qwen_0.6b_ace15.safetensors\n│   │   └── qwen_1.7b_ace15.safetensors\n│   └── 📂 vae/\n│       └── ace_1.5_vae.safetensors\n```\n\n"],"color":"#222","bgcolor":"#000"},{"id":111,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[713.4398696148143,-1104.6883149858795],"size":[254.08711093161412,200.41490576198646],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Lyrics Tag","properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.5.1","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["### 가사 구조 태그\n- [intro]\n- [verse]\n- [pre-chorus]\n- [chorus]\n- [bridge]\n- [outro]\n- [hook]\n- [refrain]\n- [interlude]\n- [breakdown]\n- [ad-lib]"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":94,"type":"TextEncodeAceStepAudio1.5","pos":[270,-790],"size":[611.9184354063266,679.7643386829468],"flags":{},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":261},{"localized_name":"tags","name":"tags","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"tags"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"lyrics","name":"lyrics","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"lyrics"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"seed","name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":257},{"localized_name":"bpm","name":"bpm","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"bpm"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"duration","name":"duration","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"duration"},"link":251},{"localized_name":"timesignature","name":"timesignature","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"timesignature"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"language","name":"language","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"language"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"keyscale","name":"keyscale","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"keyscale"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"generate_audio_codes","name":"generate_audio_codes","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"generate_audio_codes"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"cfg_scale","name":"cfg_scale","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"cfg_scale"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"temperature","name":"temperature","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"temperature"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"top_p","name":"top_p","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"top_p"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"top_k","name":"top_k","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"top_k"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"min_p","name":"min_p","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"min_p"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"CONDITIONING","name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[254,255]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.11.1","Node name for S&R":"TextEncodeAceStepAudio1.5","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"seed":true,"duration":true},"version":"7.5.1","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["K-pop sentimental ballad with a female lead vocal. A warm, emotional track built around piano and soft strings, starting intimate and minimal, then gradually expanding with subtle drums and layered harmonies. The song should feel nostalgic and heartfelt, focusing on longing, memories, and quiet hope. The vocal performance is expressive and delicate in the verses, growing more powerful and emotional in the chorus, with a cinematic yet restrained climax. Tempo is slow to mid-tempo, mood is melancholic but comforting, suitable for late-night listening.","[Intro]\n불 꺼진 방, 남은 공기\n아직도 네가 있는 것 같아\n\n[Verse 1]\n시계 소리만 커지는 밤\n괜히 네 이름을 불러 보다\n대답 없는 이 침묵 속에\n혼자 웃다가 또 울어\n\n우리가 걷던 그 길 위엔\n지워지지 않는 흔적들\n잊으려 할수록 더 선명해\n마음에 비처럼 번져 가\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\n잘 지내고 있니, 그 한마디가\n왜 이렇게 먼 말인지\n목 끝까지 차오른 그 말\n오늘도 그냥 삼켜\n\n[Chorus]\n아직도 나는 너를 불러\n시간이 멈춘 것처럼\n사랑이란 이름 아래\n우린 서로를 놓쳤나 봐\n\n하루가 지나가도\n계절이 바뀌어 가도\n내 마음은 그날에\n여전히 너를 기다려\n\n[Verse 2]\n괜찮은 척 웃어 보지만\n눈물은 늘 더 솔직해\n잊어야 한다는 말들이\n나를 더 아프게 해\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\n혹시라도 이 노래가\n너에게 닿는다면\n한 번쯤은 뒤돌아봐 줘\n우리가 있던 순간\n\n[Chorus]\n아직도 나는 너를 불러\n꿈에서라도 괜찮아\n닿을 수 없는 곳이라도\n너는 나의 전부였어\n\n하루가 무너져도\n세상이 등을 돌려도\n내 마음은 그 자리에\n여전히 너를 안고 있어\n\n[Bridge]\n사랑은 왜 항상\n늦게서야 알게 될까\n붙잡을 수 없단 걸\n이제서야 배워\n\n[Final Chorus]\n이제는 너를 보내줄게\n눈물로 적신 이 밤에\n사랑이란 이름으로\n너를 놓아줄 수 있게\n\n그래도 기억해 줘\n우리가 빛나던 날\n내 전부였던 너를\n끝까지 사랑했다고\n\n[Outro]\n조용히 밝아 오는 아침\n이제는… 안녕이라고 말할게",31,"fixed",72,120,"4","ko","E minor",true,2,0.85,0.9,0,0]},{"id":104,"type":"UNETLoader","pos":[-170,-790],"size":[380,82],"flags":{},"order":2,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"unet_name","name":"unet_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"unet_name"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"weight_dtype","name":"weight_dtype","typ